params._nftCollectionAddress: Collection address of the given NFT
params._nftTokenID: Token ID of the given NFT

getCurrentHighestBidder(address,uint256).details: Call this function when you want to know the address of the highest bidder

params._nftTokenID: Token ID of the given NFT

getTotalBid(address,uint256).details: Call this function from the front to know how mush the bidder already bidded

params._nftCollectionAddress: Collection address of the given NFT
